    "description": "Kitakei Co., Ltd. engages in the sale and installation of new building materials, housing equipment, and other products in Japan. It provides wooden building materials, including interiors doors, closets, floors, system storage, and staircase sets; non-wood building materials, such as gypsum board, insulation, roofing materials, non-combustible board, and siding products; and Lauan and softwood plywood products. The company also offers wood products comprising wood structural and construction materials, flooring, and laminated boards; housing equipment, including system kitchen, unit bath, vanities, toilet, air conditioning equipment, combustion equipment, and solar panels; and other products, such as sashes, exteriors, chemical products, and architectural hardware and tools. In addition, it is involved in the construction of exterior walls, housing, roof, structural frame, interior, and sash; and solar power generation system, as well as provision of ancillary services. The company offers its products to lumber stores, building material stores, construction companies, housing companies, etc. Kitakei Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1950 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
